plot: Franco spends his last days of life in &"El Palacio del Pardo&", between delusions of the past, and surrounded by his family and his loyal military entourage. These, desperate for the delicate state of health of the Caudillo, decide to resort to alternative medicine Dr. Müller, a modern German woman, to the astonishment of all, ending will be determined by becoming the right hand of Generalísimo.   Written by  Karmencita
